being pushed to take an easier path for me.

286
00:14:57,570 --> 00:14:58,630
Then do you like it?

287
00:15:05,990 --> 00:15:06,810
I don't know.

288
00:15:07,950 --> 00:15:09,050
In my childhood,

289
